"content": "<h2>Bricks used in construction</h2>\n<h3>The tower of Babel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:3-Gen11:4\">GEN 11:3–11:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Altars</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:3\">ISA 65:3</a></p>\n<h3>Pavements</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:9\">JER 43:9</a></p>\n<h3>Bricks were cheaper than stone</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:10\">ISA 9:10</a></p>\n<h3>Repair of brickwork</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:14\">NAM 3:14</a></p>\n<h2>Making bricks as a punishment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:14\">EXO 1:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:30-2Sam12:31\">2SA 12:30–12:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:7-Exod5:19\">EXO 5:7–5:19</a></p>",
